c: 3
v: 41
t: "Nabii Zakariyya Yi-Rabbow Yi- Barra Baxal tussukuqqem elle Aaxige Asta yoh ab iyye, Yalli kaal gacisak Asta kok atu Sidiica Ayrooy Sidiica Barih gide Sinaamâ luk yabtam duude wayya haytaama Ascossil keenil luk yabta koo Akke waytek Atu Nagay Qaafiyatah Anuk, atu isi Rabbi maggom cusaay carraay Saaku Salat kaah Ab kaak iyye Yalli"